results.name: Permutation of natural numbers generated by 6-rowed array shown below.
comment: For such arrays A_k, here A_6, see a W. Lang comment on A113807, the A_7 case. However, to get the array A_6 one should take the last line as the first one and add a 0 in front (thus obtaining a permutation of the nonnegative integers). - From Wolfdieter Lang, Feb 02 2012
